<Layout title="Conveyancing in Queensland: Solicitor or Licensed Conveyancer When Selling? | Daniel Gierach Property" description="When selling property in Queensland, you need a conveyancer or solicitor to handle the legal side. Here is how to choose the right one for your sale." draft={draft}>

